    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute dream and in truly flawless condition\u2014it's been babied since day one! It drives like a charm and looks even better in person. I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love instantly. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
